Class User

java.lang.Object
model.User
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class User extends Object implements Serializable
The User class represents a user that contains a collection of albums. It provides functionality to manage albums and retrieve user details.

This class implements Serializable to allow serialization of album objects.

Features of the Album class include:

  • Adding and removing albums
  • Managing instance fields
